---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ConsultationCTA from '@/components/ConsultationCTA.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Surfaces & Materials — Pronorm USA",
  "description": "Explore Pronorm's extensive range of front surfaces and materials: ultra-matte lacquer, high-gloss, real wood veneer, organic glass, textured laminates, and the 2026 collection.",
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Surfaces & Materials"
  description="Pronorm surfaces and materials — ultra-matte lacquer, high-gloss, real wood veneer, organic glass, textured laminates, and the 2026 collection. Over 100 door options."
  schema={schema}
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero" style="position:relative; overflow:hidden;">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/images/product-lines/category-material.jpg');background-size:cover;background-position:center;opacity:0.12;"></div>
    <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
      <span class="overline animate-in">Surfaces &amp; Materials</span>
      <h1 class="animate-in animate-in-delay-1">Touch, See,<br/>Feel the Difference</h1>
      <p class="subtitle animate-in animate-in-delay-2" style="max-width: 55ch;">
        Over 100 door front options spanning lacquers, veneers, laminates, and organic glass — all manufactured to identical quality standards and rigorously tested for daily use.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Surface Categories -->
  <section class="section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
        <span class="overline">Front Types</span>
        <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Every Surface, One Standard</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="surface-types">

        <div class="surface-type reveal">
          <div class="surface-type-header">
            <h3>Ultra-Matte Lacquer</h3>
            <span class="surface-badge">Anti-Fingerprint</span>
          </div>
          <p>A special UV lacquer applied to a melamine resin layer creates outstanding surface smoothness and an impression of depth. Anti-fingerprint properties reduce cleaning frequency and provide a warm, soft feel. PP thick edging applied all-round in the front colour.</p>
          <div class="surface-features">
            <span>Soft tactile feel</span>
            <span>Anti-fingerprint</span>
            <span>UV-stable</span>
            <span>Scratch-resistant</span>
          </div>
          <div class="swatch-row">
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#f5f3ef;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Arctic White</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#d6cbba;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Sand</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#c8bfb0;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Sahara Beige</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#b5aca0;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Angora Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#a09890;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Quartz Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#8a8480;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Platin Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#5a5550;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Carbon Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#2a2826;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Black</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="surface-type reveal">
          <div class="surface-type-header">
            <h3>High-Gloss Lacquer</h3>
            <span class="surface-badge">Seamless Edges</span>
          </div>
          <p>MDF substrate guarantees a perfectly smooth surface. Edges are lacquered in-process for a seamless transition — no visible edge banding. The multilayer lacquer structure is particularly characterized by exceptional durability.</p>
          <div class="surface-features">
            <span>Mirror-like finish</span>
            <span>Lacquered edges</span>
            <span>MDF substrate</span>
            <span>Multilayer durability</span>
          </div>
          <div class="swatch-row">
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #ddd;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Super White</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#f2ece0;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Magnolia</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#a8a29e;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Stone Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#706b66;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Cubanit</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#2e2b28;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Havana Black</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="surface-type reveal">
          <div class="surface-type-header">
            <h3>UV-Lacquer</h3>
            <span class="surface-badge">Colour-Matched Edging</span>
          </div>
          <p>MDF base with melamine coating on both sides, the front side multilayered with UV lacquer and finished with all-round colour-matching thick edging. UV-lacquered fronts attain their final colour once the protective foil is removed and after exposure to natural light.</p>
          <div class="surface-features">
            <span>Rich colour depth</span>
            <span>Light-reactive</span>
            <span>Colour-matched</span>
            <span>Durable finish</span>
          </div>
          <div class="swatch-row">
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#f5f3ef;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Arctic White</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#f2ece0;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Magnolia</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#8e2a2a;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Carmine Red</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#7b8978;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Grey-Green</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#3d4f5f;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Blue-Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#a8a29e;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Stone Grey</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="surface-type reveal">
          <div class="surface-type-header">
            <h3>Real Wood Veneer</h3>
            <span class="surface-badge">Natural Character</span>
          </div>
          <p>Only specially chosen wood is used for veneered fronts, sealed internally and externally with a special surface treatment. Available in oak, walnut, and specialty species. Each front has unique natural grain variation — lending individual character to every kitchen.</p>
          <div class="surface-features">
            <span>Natural grain</span>
            <span>Sealed both sides</span>
            <span>Easy to clean</span>
            <span>Hard-wearing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="swatch-row">
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c8a87c,#d4b88a);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Oak Natural</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d1c4a8,#c5b898);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Oak Cashmere</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8a7560,#7d6b55);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Oak Truffle Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6b5b4a,#5e503e);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Oak Sepia</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5c4a3a,#4e3e30);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Smoked Oak</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5a4535,#4d3a2c);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Walnut</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="surface-type reveal">
          <div class="surface-type-header">
            <h3>Organic Glass</h3>
            <span class="surface-badge">Scratch-Resistant</span>
          </div>
          <p>High-quality wooden panels coated on both sides with 2mm thick PMMA panels (Rauvisio Crystal). Completely seamless fronts with high scratch resistance and an anti-fingerprint lacquer surface. UV-stable and non-warping due to symmetrical construction.</p>
          <div class="surface-features">
            <span>2mm PMMA</span>
            <span>Seamless</span>
            <span>Non-warping</span>
            <span>UV-stable</span>
          </div>
          <div class="swatch-row">
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#f5f3ef;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Arctic White</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#b8b2ab;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Stratus Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#c4b8a8;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Platin</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#5e5850;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Onyx Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#2a2826;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Black</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="surface-type reveal">
          <div class="surface-type-header">
            <h3>Synthetic Layered</h3>
            <span class="surface-badge">Value Range</span>
          </div>
          <p>High-quality three-layer chipboard or MDF substrate with premium synthetic layer surfaces. Extensive colour and texture range from smooth solids to wood-effect decors. An excellent balance of design choice, durability, and value.</p>
          <div class="surface-features">
            <span>Wide colour range</span>
            <span>Texture options</span>
            <span>Three-layer board</span>
            <span>Cost-effective</span>
          </div>
          <div class="swatch-row">
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #ddd;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Super White</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#f2ece0;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Magnolia</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#d6cbba;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Sand</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c8a87c,#d4b88a);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Denver Oak</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8a8078,#7d746c);" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Agate Grey</span></div>
            <div class="swatch"><div style="background:#2e2b28;" class="swatch-circle"></div><span>Havana Black</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2026 Collection -->
  <section class="section bg-ivory">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
        <span class="overline">2026 Collection</span>
        <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">New Surfaces, Textures &amp; Colours</h2>
        <p class="subtitle" style="margin: 1rem auto 0; max-width: 55ch;">From finely textured Boho-style surfaces and woven linen-look designs to veneered fronts with intricate fan structures — the 2026 collection brings unprecedented tactile and visual depth.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="trend-grid">
        <div class="trend-card reveal">
          <img src="/images/surfaces/trends-2026-boho-natural.webp" alt="Boho Texture surface" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px;" />
          <h4>Boho Texture</h4>
          <p>Finely textured relief surface with natural, organic character.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trend-card reveal">
          <img src="/images/surfaces/trends-2026-ribbed-surface.webp" alt="Ribbed Painted Wood surface" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px;" />
          <h4>Ribbed Painted Wood</h4>
          <p>Fluted lacquered surface with elegant vertical ribbing that catches and plays with light.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trend-card reveal">
          <img src="/images/surfaces/trends-2026-buffalo-mocha.webp" alt="Buffalo Leather surface" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px;" />
          <h4>Buffalo Leather</h4>
          <p>Rich natural leather-look front with warm, tactile character.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl);">
        <a href="/request-consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Request Material Samples</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Construction Quality -->
  <section class="section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-split">
        <div class="content-text reveal">
          <span class="overline">Construction</span>
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">What's Behind<br/>Every Surface</h2>
          <hr class="divider" style="margin: 1.5rem 0;" />
          <p>Regardless of the front finish you choose, every Pronorm surface shares the same construction principles: colour-matched edgebanding on doors in almost every colour, carcass interiors finished in white, gray, or colour-matched to the front, PUR-bonded adhesive edges for superior moisture and heat resistance, and E05-class formaldehyde emissions (0.05 ppm — well below regulatory limits).</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Finished ends with white interiors are available across nearly the entire range, giving exposed cabinet sides a clean, integrated look. Every finish is rigorously tested for UV resistance, scratch hardness, impact resistance, and daily-use durability before it enters the collection.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-image reveal">
          <img src="/images/equipment/carcase-interior-metal.jpg" alt="Carcase interior quality" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/3;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ConsultationCTA />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { padding: var(--space-5xl) 0 var(--space-2xl); }

  .content-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-4xl); align-items: center; }

  .surface-types {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .surface-type {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-ivory);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-copper);
  }

  .surface-type-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .surface-type-header h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 0; }

  .surface-badge {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    background: var(--color-copper);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .surface-type p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-graphite); }

  .surface-features {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .surface-features span {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-sand);
    color: var(--color-graphite);
  }

  .swatch-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-sand);
  }

  .swatch {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .swatch-circle {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .swatch span {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--color-warm-gray);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 60px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .trend-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--space-xl); }
  .trend-card h4 { margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .trend-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-graphite); margin-top: 0.25rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .trend-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .surface-type { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
